How to cite / attribute:

If you use this repository, please cite the accompanying Neurocomputing paper
(see CITATION in README.md) and link back to this repository.

Third-party data note:
The external-replication results use latency measurements from the nn-Meter
dataset (Microsoft, MobiSys 2021), which is distributed under its own license
by its authors. Only derived summary CSVs are included here; the raw nn-Meter
files must be obtained from the official nn-Meter release and remain subject to
their original terms.
